@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
# Run requests in order so the session cookie is reused (VS Code REST Client).
# Or run: node verify-auth-api.mjs (starts its own server)

### Health (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### DB check without login — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-check

### Login player1
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "player2",
  "password": "password"
}

### Current user (use cookie from login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/current

### DB check with session cookie
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-check

### Network full (setup map)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/network?view=full

### Network planning (stations only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/network?view=planning

### All segment pairs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/segments

### Logout
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/current

### Current user after logout — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/current
